room_title: Escape room "Kidnapped Part III" by Escape Today in Owensboro
room_description: He's back, and with more tricks up his sleeve. In this new chapter to the Kidnapped series you find your group both split up and trapped in another series of frightening challenges. The barn you find yourself in contains the remnants of numerous victims. Can you reunite your group all while dodging the Kidnapper's constant check-ins? Find out in Kidnapped Part III!
